content: Dr. Wendy Li joined Gracell as the Chief Medical Officer on August 1, and she is based in the U.S. Dr. Li will oversee Gracell's clinical development activities, including advancement of our rich pipeline of autologous and allogeneic product candidates across the FasTCAR and TruUCAR technology platforms.
